Demo of Amstrad CPC+ sprites by Arnaud for CPCTelera, and about WinCpctelera

   2019-07-29 14:22 - Genesis8

   Arnaud Bouche is the author of Bitume inspired of Asphalt and Deeper
   Warrens inspired of the classic gauntlet with some RPG elements.

   He is also the author of the WinCpctelera utility which lets you
   program quickly under windows a program using the CPCTelera framework
   which will compile also on Amstrad CPC with this CPCTelera library.

   And it's with CPCTelera that he programmed a demo of Amstrad CPC+
   sprites.

   Source : CPCWiki

   Related news about Arnaud Bouche :
