   2019-06-30 16:33 - Genesis8

   David Given who is the author of CP/Mish (CP/M for Notepad NC200 using
   disk drive) did obtain from Richard Russel author of the Z80 BBC Basic
   that this version becames open source (Zlib license) and so available
   on CP/MIsh's github.

   You can read the history of the BBC Basic on Richard Russell's web
   site.

